ass=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is not just a story of simple revenge; </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >it is a battle of wits, an open conspiracy, and a grand layout. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is time to turn the tables, reverse your destiny, and take back what is yours.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Characters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103060/extras/ec62c9df0c32939b3c82b11ba89137b9.poster.avif?t=1770390545\" width=1170 height=878 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103060/extras/ec62c9df0c32939b3c82b11ba89137b9.webm?t=1770390545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103060/extras/ec62c9df0c32939b3c82b11ba89137b9.mp4?t=1770390545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Su Yuan:</strong> A university senior who appears innocent and harmless. It was her accusation years ago that single-handedly shattered your peaceful life and cast you into the abyss.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103060/extras/1e7e33d0e54a0c5f9ccd7d6f7e88698a.poster.avif?t=1770390545\" width=1170 height=878 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103060/extras/1e7e33d0e54a0c5f9ccd7d6f7e88698a.webm?t=1770390545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103060/extras/1e7e33d0e54a0c5f9ccd7d6f7e88698a.mp4?t=1770390545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Zhou Haiyi:</strong> Hailed as the &quot;Rose of the Scales,&quot; she is a star judge and a leading figure in Jiangzhou. The presiding judge who biasedly sealed your fate and sentenced you to prison is now a towering, seemingly insurmountable wall standing between you and your revenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103060/extras/1fd581c228d394c384b82987367fc5a7.poster.avif?t=1770390545\" width=1170 height=878 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103060/extras/1fd581c228d394c384b82987367fc5a7.webm?t=1770390545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103060/extras/1fd581c228d394c384b82987367fc5a7.mp4?t=1770390545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Zhong Qianxue:</strong> The young Chairwoman of a renowned real estate group in Jiangzhou. Beneath her glamorous facade, she appears to be single-handedly holding up a crumbling empire on the brink of collapse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103060/extras/1c2c093fa23c637464d3395bf57097cb.poster.avif?t=1770390545\" width=1170 height=878 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103060/extras/1c2c093fa23c637464d3395bf57097cb.webm?t=1770390545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103060/extras/1c2c093fa23c637464d3395bf57097cb.mp4?t=1770390545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fang Ning:</strong> Zhong Qianxue's best friend and a fiery elite lawyer. She treats you with hostility from the moment you meet, yet the legal idol she worships turns out to be...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. A gripping, twisting revenge story with over 100,000 words of text. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. All main characters feature multiple outfits and animated character sprites. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. Supports up to 4K resolution, bringing every detail of your revenge to life. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. Your choices will determine the final outcome.</p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>From a top student to a prisoner—how quickly can a life be ruined?</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a decade of relentless studying, you made it to the prestigious Jiangzhou University. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But your bright future was extinguished in the library, where you were framed by a manipulative senior student looking to secure her own academic success at your expense. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sentenced by a biased judge and condemned by public opinion, you lost everything.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are Xiao Wen (renamable), a 19-year-old introverted scholar whose future was stolen. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now, released early from prison, you are no longer the naive boy who couldn't defend himself in court. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have returned from hell with nothing but the ruthless skills you learned inside.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is not just a story of simple revenge; </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >it is a battle of wits, an open conspiracy, and a grand layout. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is time to turn the tables, reverse your destiny, and take back what is yours.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Characters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/st